#: ../../12-document.md:1 37a06d6f6f6e4c5da5c98d47d36cc095
msgid "Lazy Todo App — Generating the Project Knowledge Base"
msgstr "Lazy Todo App — 生成项目知识库"

#: ../../12-document.md:5 dc3c07ebda404c37846811974aee5f8d
msgid "Purpose"
msgstr "目的"

#: ../../12-document.md:7 ba75bfcc07fb4396bf39d9ef29dd74d2
msgid ""
"This page explains how to create, update, translate, and publish the "
"Project Knowledge Base (PKB) for `lazy-todo-app`."
msgstr "本页说明如何为 `lazy-todo-app` 创建、更新、翻译并发布项目知识库（PKB）。"

#: ../../12-document.md:9 04f28e01d7ec4600aff04953e03455fe
msgid ""
"In this repository, the PKB lives directly under `doc/`. English Markdown"
" is the source of truth, the content is often drafted or updated with an "
"LLM plus documentation skills, and the published site is built with "
"`Sphinx + MyST + sphinx-intl + Mermaid`."
msgstr ""
"在这个仓库中，PKB 直接位于 `doc/` 下。英文 Markdown 是事实来源，文档内容通常通过 LLM "
"配合文档技能起草或更新，最终发布站点使用 `Sphinx + MyST + sphinx-intl + Mermaid` 构建。"

#: ../../12-document.md:11 9043a18930ee4950bbea169ce1695cf4
msgid "The current documentation workflow combines:"
msgstr "当前的文档工作流结合了："

#: ../../12-document.md:13 101f6dd1117e4bd688c453e451a8aa10
msgid "an LLM to analyze the repo and draft PKB pages"
msgstr "使用 LLM 分析仓库并起草 PKB 页面"

#: ../../12-document.md:14 1f02accb951744a9bcbb5c7f84474808
msgid ""
"skills such as the Project Knowledge Base skill to enforce structure and "
"conventions"
msgstr "使用诸如 Project Knowledge Base skill 之类的技能来约束结构和规范"

#: ../../12-document.md:15 d2683d2c0a3f4178accddaa0481465c8
msgid "human review to correct intent, wording, and architectural judgment"
msgstr "通过人工审阅修正文档意图、表述和架构判断"

#: ../../12-document.md:16 0312e78b866344abbedb84d5dbb93be5
msgid "Sphinx tooling to build bilingual HTML output"
msgstr "使用 Sphinx 工具链构建双语 HTML 输出"

#: ../../12-document.md:18 d712a32ae2504fa1a080e5fbbb3efd5d
msgid "LLM + Skills Workflow"
msgstr "LLM + Skills 工作流"

#: ../../12-document.md:20 a7ae7fca9d4249b3a3d129f6ba695c02
msgid ""
"For this project, PKB pages are typically generated or updated through an"
" LLM-assisted workflow rather than written fully by hand from scratch."
msgstr "在这个项目中，PKB 页面通常通过 LLM 辅助工作流生成或更新，而不是完全从零手工编写。"

#: ../../12-document.md:22 07c1b77e7f6e4deb8c1c43471ef3f007
msgid "The practical flow is:"
msgstr "实际流程如下："

#: ../../12-document.md:24 f11f760b66744f0ba7046297ac41d6b6
msgid "The LLM reads the repository structure, key configs, and existing docs."
msgstr "LLM 读取仓库结构、关键配置和现有文档。"

#: ../../12-document.md:25 2f433613f23e46c9bdf9c9cfcbedbd47
msgid ""
"A documentation skill such as the Project Knowledge Base skill helps "
"structure the output into PKB pages like overview, repo map, "
"architecture, workflows, runbook, and testing docs."
msgstr ""
"像 Project Knowledge Base skill 这样的文档技能会帮助把输出组织成 overview、repo "
"map、architecture、workflows、runbook 和 testing 等 PKB 页面。"

#: ../../12-document.md:26 0f5fd259cf6445408b7052d430c99425
msgid "The generated Markdown is written into `doc/` as English source pages."
msgstr "生成的 Markdown 会作为英文源页面写入 `doc/`。"

#: ../../12-document.md:27 466c6247ebe7406ebe7a1137f84c2792
msgid ""
"A human reviews and edits the result to make sure the \"why\", "
"terminology, and product intent are correct."
msgstr "随后由人工审阅和修改结果，以确保文档中的“为什么”、术语和产品意图都是正确的。"

#: ../../12-document.md:28 89d1c70cc26340b9bbe30f0b42752daf
msgid ""
"The docs are translated through gettext catalogs and then built into the "
"bilingual site with `Sphinx + MyST + sphinx-intl`."
msgstr "文档通过 gettext catalog 进行翻译，然后使用 `Sphinx + MyST + sphinx-intl` 构建成双语站点。"

#: ../../12-document.md:29 5fe41b2773894c2bb148411da6d27fc3
msgid ""
"Mermaid diagrams are used when workflows or architecture benefit from "
"visual explanation."
msgstr "当工作流或架构需要可视化说明时，会使用 Mermaid 图。"

#: ../../12-document.md:31 cdec2e1d45954ae999a8950e3e020714
msgid ""
"This means the PKB should be treated as human-reviewed, AI-assisted "
"documentation. The LLM is responsible for fast synthesis and structure; "
"the human is responsible for validating accuracy, intent, and trade-offs."
msgstr "这意味着 PKB 应该被视为“人工审阅、AI 辅助”的文档。LLM 负责快速归纳和组织结构；人工则负责验证准确性、意图和取舍。"

#: ../../12-document.md:33 ce6195f6cfee4aed86127eb853989773
msgid "Advisory Auto-Update Loop"
msgstr "告警式自动更新循环"

#: ../../12-document.md:35 62846632b72441c88b1211419810a898
msgid ""
"Today, this repository uses an advisory PKB update loop rather than a "
"fully automatic doc-writing bot."
msgstr "当前，这个仓库采用的是告警式 PKB 更新循环，而不是全自动写文档机器人。"

#: ../../12-document.md:37 93f7d334f73449388b93cb8b143ddd57
msgid "The implemented pieces are:"
msgstr "当前已实现的组成部分包括："

#: ../../12-document.md:39 fcb8f0e6040f4c99a30d6d7a9768e5c3
msgid "`scripts/check_pkb_staleness.py` for rule-based PKB impact analysis"
msgstr "`scripts/check_pkb_staleness.py` 用于基于规则的 PKB 影响分析"

#: ../../12-document.md:40 77c18b93e41f4dc5bccf79e564619e31
msgid "`npm run pkb:check` for local advisory checks"
msgstr "`npm run pkb:check` 用于本地告警检查"

#: ../../12-document.md:41 ed189b43598e476e9fe3872173119c7c
msgid ""
"`/.github/workflows/pkb-check.yml` for PR and branch summaries in GitHub "
"Actions"
msgstr "`/.github/workflows/pkb-check.yml` 用于在 GitHub Actions 中生成 PR 和分支摘要"

#: ../../12-document.md:43 afbf1064fc6648ba897a1b5865bfe520
msgid "The current loop works like this:"
msgstr "当前循环的工作方式如下："

#: ../../12-document.md:45 2e0b061a40ab4bfb8c4f60aafc4922fc
msgid "Code, workflow, or configuration changes land in a branch or pull request."
msgstr ""

#: ../../12-document.md:46 aac847b035fc4ba4aeb70e504dfb18ea
msgid "The PKB checker maps changed files to likely-affected PKB pages."
msgstr ""

#: ../../12-document.md:47 864b8288760f4c60ae83c7d49eb1ece1
msgid "The checker reports whether those PKB pages were updated in the same diff."
msgstr ""

#: ../../12-document.md:48 c478c1dc83064a3b8c6745a58b51332a
msgid ""
"A human uses the summary to decide which English PKB pages should be "
"refreshed."
msgstr ""

#: ../../12-document.md:49 7dcf33b8faf943358fb545c6701d2a02
msgid ""
"The LLM plus documentation skills can then draft the updated English PKB "
"content."
msgstr ""

#: ../../12-document.md:50 1b68e382bf3b4954b1ecd6477db86074
msgid "A human reviews the generated Markdown before translation and publishing."
msgstr ""

#: ../../12-document.md:52 f20b71d6664541a5b8f74c420d661936
msgid ""
"The important design rule is that the checker is deterministic, but the "
"actual documentation refresh still happens through the human-reviewed LLM"
" + skills workflow."
msgstr "一个重要设计原则是：检查器本身应保持确定性，但真正的文档刷新仍然通过“人工审阅的 LLM + skills 工作流”完成。"

